wabe_Shikwa_Award.jpg|alt=|center|frame]]\nThem allama iqbal famous and wall known in india mustqeem inter college gay anipursultanpur found in college Alam Ja Sultanpuri worked hard to bring this award from college be the biggest highlight of their award after allama iqbal prayer, dr anjum lucknowi answerd the question again and shikwa awesone (shikwa Jawab e Shikwa <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=889501881510943&id=100013534183110|title=Dr-Anjum Lucknowi|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-16}}</ref>) and the while world wrote praise for love.. Shikwa Jawab e Shikwa a poem...\n\n==Book==\n\u2022''Azmat E Maan-(2014) Public''\n\n[[File:Azmat_E_Maan_Book.jpg|alt=|border|frameless|207x207px]]\n\n\n\n\u2022''[[:File:Shikwa Jawabe Shikwa Book.jpg|Shikwa jawab-E-Shikwa (2017) Publie]]''\n\n\n\n[[File:Shikwa_Jawabe_Shikwa_Book.jpg|alt=|border|frameless|171x171px]]\n\n\n\u2022''Zarb-E-Moosa'' ''Coming Soon....''\n\n[[File:Zarb_E_Moosa_Book.jpg|alt=|border|frameless|199x199px]]\n\n== Book opening ==\nAzmat-E-Maan  Opening [[Quaiser Khalid]] IPS With [[Salma Agha]]\n[[File:Azmat_E_Maan.jpg|alt=|center]]\nOpening of Azmat e Maan IPS Qaiser Khalid and Salma Aga did Opening the first book The dargah took place in Daragah Sheikh Misri Antop Hill Wadala Mumbai \n[[File:Allama_Iqbal_Award.jpg|alt=|frame]]\nShikwa Jawabe Shikwa Opening\nAnd the second book's Ie Shikwa Jawab e Shikwa Opening Mustaqim inter college Giani Pur Sultanpur Uttar Pradesh And was awarded the Allama Iqbal Award at Mustaqim Inter College [ Mustaqeem Inter College Gayanipur Sultanpur UP]\n\n==Favorite poetry==\n[[File:Allama Iqbal.jpg|thumb|210x210px|Dr Allama Iqbal ]]\nLucknowi most favorite poetry '''''[[Muhammad Iqbal|Dr Allama Iqbal]]''''' most like Believing Allama Iqbal to be his master in his life, he followed his footsteps and shared a poetry list like him and his...Allama Iqbal's Shikwa became famous in the world, which was the first Shikwa and the second Shikwa.. Anjum Lucknowi wrote  Shikwa, he had thought that I will write the second 2 number Shikwa in the world i.e. Anjum Lucknowi And he did this by the second number...As a child, he was very much in love with Allama Iqbal, he had to walk on the path of Allama Iqbal...The strange thing is that Anjum lucknowi real name is also Iqbal Khan..\n\n== Famous Poetry ==\nDr Anjum Lucknowi also gets a name in big cities of the world.For example, Anjum Rahbar IPS Qaisera Khalid and Hasan Kamal Like these are also mentioned in cities..For example, this is the page in the images world that book refers to the famous poet of all the famous poet.\n\n[[File:Famous Poetr.jpg|thumb|310x310px|World Book Only Single Sentence Of Poem]]\n[[Anjum Rehbar|Anjum Rahbar]] Or [[Dr Anjum Lucknowi]] Or [[Quaiser Khalid]] Or [[Hasan Kamal|hasan kamaal]] etc...\n\n==Student==\n\nAktar Allahabad, Maulana Makki Ashraf Qadri, Ateeq Maheshar Barabankavi,Shadab Anwar, Afraz Siddharth Nagari, Yusuf Rana, Faizan Kanpuri,Ali Ahmed Nizami, Qayyum Danish, Asad Ullah Asad, Nehal Azmi, Hassan Sahir, Imran Sahiba, Moin Sadiq, Faiz Gorakhpur, Asad Bastavi, Maulana Aish Akhtar Bastavi, Alim ja sultanpuri....more 144 it is Popular Student\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.facebook.com/people/Dr-Anjum-Lucknowi/100013534183110 Facebook]\n*[https://twitter.com/lucknowidr Twitter]\n\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lucknowi, Anjum}}\n{{Uncategorized|date=April 2020}}\n", "text_old": "{{db-spam|help=off}}\n\n'''<big>Dr Anjum Lucknowi</big>'''\nWorld i want to be the biggest God poet accepted the blessings of his childhood His father '''''MOHD HALIM KHAN''''' Lathi has great masters They have over 400 students.. He also said in his life that son, Anjum Lucknowi be who you want to be. Dr. Anjum Lucknowi Real name of '''''IQBAL HALIM KHAN'''''\n<br />Some of their students 144 Is in the world of poetry\n{{Infobox writer\n| name = Anjum Lucknowi <br />{{lang|ur|{{Nastaliq|\u0627\u0646\u06